import { createApp } from 'vue/dist/vue.esm-bundler'
import App from './App.vue'
import AppDescription from './components/Description.vue'
import AppGame from './components/Game.vue'
import AppMenu from './components/Menu.vue'
import * as VueRouter from 'vue-router'
import axios from 'axios'
import VueAxios from 'vue-axios'

const app = createApp(App)
const FrontOffice = app.component('front-office', require('./scripts/FrontOffice').default)
const BackOffice = app.component('back-office', require('./scripts/BackOffice').default)

app.use(FrontOffice)
app.use(BackOffice)

const routes = [
    { path: '/', component: AppMenu},
    { path: '/description', component: AppDescription },
    { path: '/game', component: AppGame },
    { path: '/services', component: {template: FrontOffice} },
    { path: '/administration', component: {template: BackOffice} }
]
const router = VueRouter.createRouter({
    history: VueRouter.createWebHistory(),
    routes
    }
)

axios.defaults.baseURL = "http://localhost:8081"
app.use(VueAxios,axios)
app.use(router)
app.mount('#app')
